Where did you put my Zhao Ling'er keychain?

36
00:02:39,630 --> 00:02:41,280
Mom.

37
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,980
Dad.

38
00:02:48,980 --> 00:02:51,360
We will be moving out soon.

39
00:02:51,870 --> 00:02:55,380
That house is big and luxurious.

40
00:02:56,280 --> 00:03:01,099
If you're still around, you would have scolded me and said I was a spendthrift.

41
00:03:02,710 --> 00:03:05,400
I won't listen to you this time.

42
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:09,149
<i>[Forever in our Memories]</i>
Since you were the one who left us behind.

43
00:03:20,590 --> 00:03:22,630
Do you see?

44
00:03:22,630 --> 00:03:26,650
Our son is very promising now.

45
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:31,460
If you were still around, you would be very proud.

46
00:03:33,590 --> 00:03:36,890
Son, salute your father.

47
00:03:36,890 --> 00:03:39,580
Do you still remember how he taught you?

48
00:03:56,560 --> 00:04:02,910
Dad, are you not willing to move because of Mom?

49
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:05,280
Even if we moved to a new place,

50
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:08,500
Mom's possessions and photos are still there. Isn't it the same?

51
00:04:08,509 --> 00:04:10,360
How can it be the same?

52
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,589
The old house is no more.

53
00:04:11,590 --> 00:04:12,959
What else can I keep in my memories?

54
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,359
All of you won't be coming back.

55
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,869
The old house is no more.

56
00:04:15,870 --> 00:04:17,630
What else can I keep in my memories?

57
00:04:26,190 --> 00:04:27,700
Dad.

58
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:32,180
I wanted to tell you this later.

59
00:04:32,830 --> 00:04:35,629
I've decided to come back and work here.

60
00:04:35,630 --> 00:04:37,679
I've found a house in Beijing.

61
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:41,259
I'm just waiting for you to move there and stay with us.

62
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:46,890
I hope you won't find us too annoying.

63
00:04:47,430 --> 00:04:49,720
Are you telling the truth?

64
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:52,040
Will your son lie to you?

65
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:56,920
In the future, no matter where you are, I'll be there with you.

66
00:05:10,180 --> 00:05:11,999
Don't touch that.

67
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,159
Remove it after watching Shiyin's show at night.

68
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,960
Come on.

69
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:20,749
She was the one who opposed our daughter learning this.

70
00:05:20,749 --> 00:05:23,890
Now, she is the one who wants to watch the show.

71
00:05:23,890 --> 00:05:25,509
Didn't you oppose it as well?

72
00:05:25,510 --> 00:05:27,030
You can just complain about me.

73
00:05:27,030 --> 00:05:30,199
Mom, I'm going out for a while.

74
00:05:30,199 --> 00:05:31,799
Why don't you leave after watching the show?

75
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,119
This is a rerun.

76
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:35,330
You have to watch it even if it's a rerun.

77
00:05:41,550 --> 00:05:44,140
